    "Secondly, an assessment of content validity and construct validity was conducted to examine the extent to which the measurement results accurately reflect the intended content.",
    "Content validity primarily reflects the breadth and richness of the scale itself.",
    "The scales used in this study were developed based on multiple previously validated scales and focus group discussions (FG), ensuring content validity.",
    "Prior to conducting exploratory analysis, a test of adequacy was performed to ensure the authenticity and effectiveness of the data.",
    "The Kaiser-Meyer-Olkin (KMO) value for the current data analysis was found to be 0.921, with an approximate chi-square value of 9680.684, degrees of freedom of 630, and a significance level of 0.000, indicating suitability for factor analysis (Balogh et al., 2001)."
